subject: Football
College Athletics
Football (College)
lead_paragraph: LaMichael James ran for 219 yards and 3 touchdowns and No. 8 Oregon (11-2) beat U.C.L.A., 49-31, in the inaugural Pac-12 title game in Eugene, Ore., for a likely berth in the Rose Bowl.
